parameters:
Would you like to view the event? Promotional activities for
health food products.

\nc<Saki>A logistics company, huh... This client seems to be smaller
in scale compared to others.

\nc<Senpai>It's considerably smaller compared to media companies and
research institutions.
\nc<Member 1>Oh, is Saki going to the logistics company this time...
\nc<Member 2>Lucky. I wanted to go this week too.
\nc<Member 1>But you went last week, didn't you?

\nc<Saki>(It might be the first time everyone wants to go to a
dispatch destination.) Dispatch work at a logistics
company... Does everyone like it?
\nc<Member 1>Of course, the work is easy and the people are kind.
\nc<Member 1>Usually sales. It's similar to what we do here.
\nc<Member 2>Meary-senpai. Is it okay if I go instead?
\nc<Senpai>Didn't you give up your turn for me last time?

\nc<Saki>(Eh... Give up? Senpai's personality is such that she would
never give up something good. Is she barely meeting her
quota? Senpai's quota is ridiculously high...)

\nc<Senpai>Saki, hurry up and go. The logistics company is close by,
you can go alone, right?

\nc<Saki>Yes! I'm on my way. (It's a shame I can't get a ride... but
it's good that the company seems easygoing.)

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>No, well, next time...(Geez, Saki. There's no way there's a
white company in our group.)
